    "  ✓ rppg_scaler.joblib\n",
    "  ✓ rppg_selector.joblib\n",
    "  ✓ best_rppg_ml_model.joblib\n",
    "  ✓ rppg_predictions.csv   ← P_rPPG for late fusion\n",
    "\n",
    "NEXT STEP — Late Fusion with CNN models:\n",
    "  See the NEW standalone fusion cell below.\n",
    "\"\"\")"
